parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the key to become stuck in the ignition, making it difficult or impossible to turn the vehicle off, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key gets stuck in the ignition
the key will not turn to the off position
the car keeps running
the key will not come out of the ignition switch
the car has to be stalled manually to stop running.
